{"TopicId":175870,"ForumId":55,"TopicTitle":"First Person Interior","CreatedByName":"IceBear730","CreatedById":189695,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-13T16:10:57Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"IceBear730","CreatedById":189695,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-13T16:10:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think that it would be really cool if you could not only go first person, but also walk/float around inside of the things you build. For example you build a complex space station, sure you can look at it and all. but what if you want to explore the inside? Even if it was a paid expansion I know people would definitely want to pay for something like that! Or maybe some mod makers would like to take advantage of the opportunity before anyone else does.\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:lol:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_laugh.png\u0022 title=\u0022:lol:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-06-13T16:12:29Z\u0022 title=\u002206/13/2018 04:12  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EJune 13, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by IceBear730\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DeltaDizzy","CreatedById":150755,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-15T00:19:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nstill WIP, but theres this, that works in at least 1.3\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed1771136588\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/118371-wip-free-iva-formerly-enhanced-iva-alpha-v003-10x-only-2015-10-11/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:225px;max-width:500px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"pandaman","CreatedById":130621,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-17T16:46:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNice idea I\u0027m \u0027on the fence\u0027 and can\u0027t vote for each.\u00A0 But I doubt it is something i would use much.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe problem i see is that, due to how ships are built, it would be difficult to have an internal structure that worked for a lot of designs.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe attach docking ports directly to fuel tanks for example, and whilst we can \u0027imagine\u0027 a tunnel to\u00A0pass through they are not modelled.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mark Kerbin","CreatedById":167193,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-28T23:27:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCool but would probs end up needing several updates and an entire dev team devoted to it and the game engine problems would be well problems... At that point you may as well just start work on ksp 2\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ncool idea tho. Would enjoy\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lisias","CreatedById":187168,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-29T01:52:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow about this:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed5268472720\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/166786-14-through-the-eyes-of-a-kerbal/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:225px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mark Kerbin","CreatedById":167193,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-29T01:55:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223407115\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022175870\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221530237175\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022187168\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Lisias\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Lisias said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow about this:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed7387800609\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/166786-14-through-the-eyes-of-a-kerbal/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:225px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe are talking in craft movement. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u00A0tks anyway cos I forgot what that mod was. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lisias","CreatedById":187168,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-29T02:15:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223407116\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022175870\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221530237352\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022167193\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Mark Kerbin\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n18 minutes ago, Mark Kerbin said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe are talking in craft movement. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhoops\u2026 I think I need to change my coffee brand\u2026 This one I\u0027m taking should be decaffeinated. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"steve_v","CreatedById":69272,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-29T05:12:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot now, due to the potential for bugs and degradation of the already miserable performance.\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nThere\u0027s also the lack of things to \u003Cem\u003Edo\u003C/em\u003E in IVA, simply floating about in a craft would get old pretty quick. If one could actually interact with things inside a spacecraft I\u0027d be more interested, but IMO it\u0027s too late in the piece to add something this big.\u003Cbr\u003E\nWe already have planetary surfaces with nothing to do on them, oceans with nothing to do in them, and buildings with nothing to do in them. Moving inside a craft strikes me as about as interesting as climbing the island control tower, I did it once and I\u0027ll never do it again.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mark Kerbin","CreatedById":167193,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-29T05:51:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo I think we as a forum have come to the general consensus that KSP needs more \u201Cscrewing around opportunities\u201D that could be in-depth but we really just want to have some actual\u00A0reason for that totally awesome and not at all pointless rover I built yesterday.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223407122\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022175870\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221530238519\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022187168\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Lisias\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, Lisias said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhoops\u2026 I think I need to change my coffee brand\u2026 This one I\u0027m taking should be decaffeinated. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd I\u2019m up at 2 am and don\u2019t even drink coffee.\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lisias","CreatedById":187168,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-29T05:53:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223407183\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022175870\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221530251465\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022167193\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Mark Kerbin\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Mark Kerbin said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd I\u2019m up at 2 am and don\u2019t even drink coffee.\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNeither do I. My coffee is so strong that I take\u00A0it with a knife,\u00A0fork and .38 in the case it tries to eat me. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-29T07:11:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI voted no just because I thought I was in another thread....\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JAFO","CreatedById":132901,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-07-09T01:16:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223407184\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022175870\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221530251611\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022187168\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Lisias\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 6/29/2018 at 3:53 PM, Lisias said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMy coffee is so strong that I take\u00A0it with a knife,\u00A0fork and .38 in the case it tries to eat me.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDamn.. and here I was thinking I was badass just because my coffee dissolves the spoon.\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u002